## Guide to install Angular Project - OSX

### Step 1:

On google type "mySQL osx homebrew" or go to this link:

### Step 2:

mkdir -p ~/Documents/workspace/microting

cd ~/Documents/workspace/microting

git clone git@github.com:microting/eform-angular-frontend.git

### Step 3:

Download and install node.JS MacOS installer [https://nodejs.org/en/download/](https://nodejs.org/en/download/)

![](data:image/png;base64,)

### Step 4: 

cd ~/Documents/workspace/microting/eform-angular-frontend/eform-client

npm install

### Step 5:

Download and install .Net core SDK for OSX [https://dotnet.microsoft.com/download](https://dotnet.microsoft.com/download)

![](data:image/png;base64,)

### Step 6:

```text
cd ~/Documents/workspace/microting/eform-angular-frontend/eFormAPI

dotnet run --project eFormAPI.Web/eFormAPI.Web.csproj
```

### Step 7:

```text
cd ~/Documents/workspace/microting/eform-angular-frontend/eform-client

npm start
```
